'''''Star Wars: Tales of the Jedi''''' is a [[Star Wars Legends|''Star Wars'' Legends]] [[Star Wars comic books|comic book]] miniseries written by [[Tom Veitch]]. It is the first volume of the eponymous [[Star Wars: Tales of the Jedi (comic series)|''Star Wars: Tales of the Jedi'']] maxiseries, and it was first published between [[1993]] and [[1994]] by [[Dark Horse Comics]]. The miniseries was later adapted into an [[Tales of the Jedi (audio drama)|audio drama]].

